Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.35,0:21:47.93,ed1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}{\1c&H0080ff80}I'm here waiting for you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.35,0:21:47.93,ed2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}{\1c&H0080ff80}{\frz-90}我在这里等待着你
